headline: Is It Too Late To Consider Waste Management After Its Strong Multi Year Share Price Run?
summary: Wondering if Waste Management is still a trash-to-treasure story at these prices, or if the easy money has already been made? Let us walk through what the market is really paying for here and whether that stacks up against the company’s fundamentals. The stock has been grinding higher, with a 1.3% gain over the last week, 1.2% over the past month, and an 8.9% rise year to date, adding to a 7.6% return over 1 year and a 101.9% return over 5 years.
